Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.02,0:01:48.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森他们想去打退海盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.99,0:01:50.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却被亚喜拉打败，经过二日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也被带上麻莫军舰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往青龙岛出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来真的是夫雷国派来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.07,0:02:06.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且身上附有恶魔，是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男人体格并不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.31,0:02:18.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他身上的愤怒精灵很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.78,0:02:24.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣，他不可以脱离精灵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.92,0:02:27.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.49,0:02:29.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.19,0:02:32.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从愤怒精灵手中解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了要和那家伙打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以又叫了回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.44,0:02:44.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱离愤怒精灵的手吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心…唤回的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.26,0:03:01.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…  可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯，你还不能动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.07,0:03:12.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了，之前是我太过轻敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.87,0:03:16.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定不会输给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，随时奉陪，小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.71,0:03:21.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定要赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.15,0:03:33.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯，你赢不了那个女战士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次，再下下次，都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用那么神气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个有学习过剑术的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎可能输给那种只有蛮力的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在剑术方面你是占上风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是实战是不一样的，明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连你也打不赢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.08,0:04:01.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你伤好之後，你还是不会赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你不要再讲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.65,0:04:06.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再讲了，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是为波里森  也不是为帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.63,0:04:15.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我的名誉  一定要打败她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的力量不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.44,0:04:26.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森居然流眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非已经有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.08,0:04:38.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉一队往青龙岛去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.99,0:04:42.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的是要得到太守的秘宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.49,0:04:44.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉让波里森一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想让波里森成为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己成功达到目的的活证人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水龙最好是拥有支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.24,0:05:01.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来亚喜拉大人的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这青龙岛将是最後一站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，在得到支配的王锡之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是真正的战争开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为还有要统一罗德岛的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是水龙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们过去  请等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.04,0:05:28.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先让我去和它协调一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.41,0:05:41.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不用打就可以拿到王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.70,0:05:58.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁扰乱我的睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他不用再讲，讲也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和人类没话可讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.41,0:06:13.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我还没生气之前，快点离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很想睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.79,0:06:20.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水龙，你守护的是支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.86,0:06:27.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是，你问完了，快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是魂的水晶球吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.84,0:06:35.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的巴格那大人终於找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.07,0:06:38.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到魂的水晶球的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:42.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是想来抢太守的秘宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.91,0:06:49.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就要毁灭你，是你的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不幸的应该是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你承认是强盗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交涉的如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.90,0:07:07.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交涉破裂，水龙没有支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们吵醒它睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它生气的要杀死我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.51,0:07:17.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法，你在这里看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欧布，你唱战歌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.12,0:07:28.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用歌去平息水龙的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.88,0:07:51.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕  想逃  这难道是恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.69,0:08:06.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最至尊的冰龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水龙面对突来的激烈攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.57,0:08:24.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火焰  大水  虽然做了反击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在亚喜拉他们的攻击下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.08,0:08:31.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量直线降低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我到底是 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.28,0:09:04.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了，你不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了   打赢了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.19,0:09:17.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赢了，可是是场无意义的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手上拿的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.38,0:09:30.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是魂之水晶球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魂的水晶球!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是太守的秘宝之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.82,0:09:37.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说可以招回死亡者的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没开始研究所以不敢确定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要和煞星龙打斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情很沉重  而你却...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅，身为魔术师的怪癖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.64,0:09:56.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想快点开始研究魂的水晶球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要回去往火龙山去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想被卡修抢先一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴格那大人，巴格那大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.79,0:10:18.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请安心，我已经拿到魂的水晶球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.03,0:10:23.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，再来就是把魂的水晶球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平安无事的拿回来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.90,0:10:30.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也别太逞强，特别是对付煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那煞星龙是古龙中的巨龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.28,0:10:37.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但亚喜拉应该可以对付它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.55,0:10:42.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好，快点回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.22,0:10:45.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点回去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不後悔利用他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要丢下他不管...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古娄达大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人请你马上去见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，我马上过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变了，你的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么讲真的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.45,0:11:18.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痊愈了，波里森，你已恢复感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.92,0:11:22.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，虽然我还不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.06,0:11:25.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种表情就是这种表情，不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要告诉他们才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了，一定要逃离这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是队长应该决定的事，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.34,0:11:38.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我们想办法，要逃一起逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.21,0:11:42.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己一个人也可以逃出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在波里森他们决定逃走的隔日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.52,0:11:50.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯林和蕾里去找莱登的军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们对队长讲所发生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.72,0:11:57.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能帮忙救出波里森他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们很担心你们的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.23,0:12:04.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也有职责所在，不能帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来只有我们自己去救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的，如果没有战士去打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.18,0:12:17.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们单纯施行魔法也没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们需要战士的援助吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很愿意帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲秘密时要细声一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声音都传到门外面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.11,0:12:49.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗，在我完全掌握住之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯，转移他的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好慢，想饿死我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.62,0:13:02.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白白让你们吃就要感谢我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的睡眠精灵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.70,0:13:12.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么  请把他带进梦中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是魔法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是魔法歌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马卢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好，有人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盗贼马卢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望里面一个人都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃走，有人逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃走的是全部吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，只有小孩一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吟游诗人吗，不用管他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.99,0:14:46.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是吟游诗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么吟游诗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是指年少的精灵一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.94,0:14:56.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们一样是属植物界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是马卢，原来他平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.38,0:15:07.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好…算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，大家都还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家有可以一起逃脱的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是讲这些的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好，让他带我们去海盗藏身所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.74,0:15:34.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，他们很厉害，会被杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佣兵王夫雷国卡修殿下在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫雷国卡修王，就是他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，带路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.52,0:15:47.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.91,0:16:21.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像天那样大，像石那样硬的火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别逃，快应战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是麻莫的部下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，我是被他雇用的船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.01,0:16:45.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我，我是卡修，你应该听过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么! 那个佣兵王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.55,0:16:51.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么夫雷国的国王会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快讲，亚喜拉他们在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.82,0:16:59.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往火龙岛去了，他是这么讲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森他们没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇定一点，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.57,0:17:10.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.98,0:17:16.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母希利斯，你受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事，伤得不重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.52,0:17:23.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要来，我们正想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道你们会这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.66,0:17:29.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为有事要做，要赶时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，那我就原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母太好了，真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来愤怒精灵的力量变弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他恢复了感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.17,0:17:44.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马卢，你居然背叛我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.57,0:17:47.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，那个时候只能那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去追亚喜拉，往火龙山云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以把支配的王锡让他拿走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.92,0:18:01.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那种身体…最好是回城里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要跟去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有个，我一定要打败的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去，去跟你学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，大家一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後将可恶的煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和亚喜拉打败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个天空是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是晚上却像黄昏一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.72,0:18:35.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非莱登火烧·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.36,0:18:41.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在又是一年杀百人的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煞星在侵袭莱登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要快点回莱登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.11,0:18:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样下去莱登的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.11,0:18:57.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再讲帕母，後果怎样我也明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在最重要就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止亚喜拉的野望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.85,0:19:05.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很痛苦，但是一定要这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.49,0:19:07.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修殿下也很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.99,0:19:14.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了一个人或为一万人着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是做国王的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.67,0:19:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要快点往火龙山去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是我们最应该做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.54,0:19:28.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了斯林，我们往火龙山去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要拿到支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.78,0:19:34.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要毁灭亚喜拉的野望